These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, roller, skateboard, train
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, trance, funk
1. the fan salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan trance##5
2. the person driving the roller is not the fan salsa##6
3. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan funk##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan trance##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan salsa##1
6. the fan salsa is not the person driving the skateboard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | roller   | train    | scooter    | skateboard |
| Sport      | funk | salsa | trance | r&b |

