.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, canadian, russian, american
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip, amaryllis, lily
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
3. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the american##5
4. the canadian is not the person who growstulip##6
5. the person who growslily is on the left of the russian##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the american is on the right of the thai##1
8. the russian is somewhere to the left of the thai##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | canadian  | russian    | thai | american    |
| Food       | lily | tulip | amaryllis  | dahlia |

