.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, may, october
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, indian, chinese, nigerian
1. the person who's birthday is in october is not the turkish##6
2. the indian is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
4. the indian is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the indian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
7. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | october       | january  | september  | may |
| Job        | chinese | nigerian | indian | turkish  |

