.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, aconite, begonia
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, mah-jongg, bridge
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
3. the person playing bridge is not the person who growsrose##6
4. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rose | aconite | begonia     | lily |
| Transport   | whist     | mah-jongg    | snooker | bridge    |

