.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, december, november
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, amaryllis, azalea
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person who growszinnia##6
3. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
4. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
7. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
8. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
9. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | april | december    | june  | november   |
| Nationality   | amaryllis  | azalea | zinnia | poppy |

