.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, milk, fanta
There 4 different types of food: potato, pepper, peas, lettuce
1. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
2. the person eating peas is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating pepper##1
4. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
5. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person eating potato##1
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fanta | sprite     | milk | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | peas | potato | lettuce      | pepper         |

