.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
City: prague, colone, rome, london
4 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, frog, fish
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
5. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
6. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
7. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
8. the person traveling to colone is not the owner of the fish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | colone  | prague        | rome      | london          |
| Job        | rat | mouse | fish | frog |

