.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, r&b, dubstep, ambient
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, fishing, rock-climbing
1. the fan pop is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the fan ambient##6
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the fan dubstep##5
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan dubstep##1
7. the fan pop is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
8. the fan r&b is somewhere to the right of the fan ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | pop  | dubstep | ambient    | r&b |
| Transport   | drawing | rock-climbing | fishing | woodworking  |

