4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, december, go
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person playing december is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person playing go and the person who's birthday is in july##2
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing snooker and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | july | october    | december | april |
| Music-Genre   | snooker         | scrabble | go   | december     |

