.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, kale, cherry, cauliflower
4 different games are played: go, billiard, monopoly, bridge
1. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
2. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing bridge is not the person eating pumpkin##6
5. the person eating cherry is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating kale##2
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
8. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | kale | cherry | pumpkin | cauliflower |
| Pet     | monopoly  | billiard      | go  | bridge       |

